sentences: Finneas Baird O'Connell (born July 30, 1997), known mononymously as Finneas, is an American singer-songwriter, record producer, and actor.

He has won eight Grammy Awards, including Album of the Year, Producer of the Year, Non-Classical and the Best Engineered Album, Non-Classical for his work on Eilish's debut album When We All Fall Asleep, Where Do We Go?
